"By internalizing key parts of the custody value chain, we are making a strategic investment in one of our most critical product areas. We are strengthening our internal capabilities, improving operational resilience, and accelerating our digital transformation. With our new partners, we are ready to provide more integrated, efficient, and future-oriented services, setting a new standard for customer-centric custody in Germany and across Europe,"

“Street food and craft beer are a real lifestyle choice” “Nowhere more so than the streets of West London. We are choosing to eat in different ways. We don’t want a fixed starter-main course-dessert menu any more — we want a bit of this and a bit of that. It’s flirty, low-commitment dining, and it’s why street food and craft beer have become so popular. WestFest, and the lifestyle it champions, will make the world a much nicer place to be”
